headline: Trimble Expands U.S. Reach via APEX Deal, Strengthening Agtech and Construction Integration
summary: Trimble (TRMB) is one of the best agriculture technology stocks to buy now. On July 22, 2025, Trimble (NASDAQ:TRMB) deepened its footprint in U.S. civil construction by naming APEX Technologies, a division of McCoy Construction & Forestry, as its newest Trimble Technology Outlet.
